  "keyFeatures": [
    "AutoML: Automatic model training, tuning, and leaderboard generation",
    "Distributed in-memory computation via DKV and MRTask",
    "Wide algorithm support: GBM, XGBoost, Random Forest, Deep Learning, GLM, GAM, K-Means, PCA, Naive Bayes, Word2Vec",
    "Stacked Ensembles for improved model performance",
    "MOJO/POJO export for low-latency production scoring",
    "Python, R, Scala, Java, and REST API clients",
    "Flow web UI for interactive data exploration and modeling",
    "Model explainability: SHAP, PDP, variable importance, residual analysis",
    "Grid search and hyperparameter tuning",
    "Hadoop, Spark (Sparkling Water), Kubernetes, and Docker support"
  ],
